<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>
<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #f7f7f7; padding: 20px;">
    <p>Hi!</p>
    <p>
        We received a request to reset the password for your Foodie account. You can easily set a new password by clicking the button below.
    </p>

    <p>
        <a href="<%= reset_url %>" style="background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Reset Your Password</a>
    </p>

    <p>
        If you're having trouble clicking the 'Reset Your Password' button, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser:
    </p>

    <p>
        <a href="<%= reset_url %>" style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: underline;"><%= reset_url %></a>
    </p>

    <p>
        If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact us if you have questions.
    </p>

    <p>
        Need help or have questions? Just shoot us an email at support@foodie.com, and we'll be right there to assist you.
    </p>

    <p>
        Happy eating!
        <br>
        <br>
        Cheers,
        <br>
        The Foodie Team
    </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>